# @canva-ct/genai

Generative AI services with LLM streaming, OpenRouter integration, fal.ai media generation, and Text-to-Speech capabilities.

## 📦 Installation

```bash
npm install @canva-ct/genai
```

## 🔐 Setup (Required)

Before using any services, you must call `setupAuth()` once at the start of your application:

```typescript
import { setupAuth } from "@canva-ct/genai";

// Call once at app startup
await setupAuth();
```

**React Example:**

```typescript
import { setupAuth } from "@canva-ct/genai";
import { useEffect } from "react";

function App() {
  useEffect(() => {
    setupAuth();
  }, []);

  return <YourApp />;
}
```

This function:

- Initializes authentication with `@canva-ct/auth`
- Fetches the GenAI service configuration from Canva playground
- Must complete before any AI service calls will work

