## 🚀 AIService (Recommended)

The `AIService` provides a unified interface for all GenAI capabilities with automatic routing.

```typescript
import { AIService } from "@canva-ct/genai";

const ai = new AIService({ defaultModel: "openai/gpt-4o" });
```

### Available Models

| Provider   | Models                                                     |
| ---------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- |
| Google     | `google/gemini-2.5-flash`, `google/gemini-2.5-pro`         |
| Anthropic  | `anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5`, `anthropic/claude-opus-4.1` |
| OpenAI     | `openai/gpt-5`, `openai/gpt-5-mini`                        |
| Perplexity | `perplexity/sonar-reasoning-pro`, `perplexity/sonar-pro`   |

Full list: [OpenRouter Models](https://openrouter.ai/models)

### Methods

#### `chat(request, callbacks?)` - Chat with AI

```typescript
// Simple chat
const response = await ai.chat({
  messages: [{ role: "user", content: "Hello!" }],
  model: "openai/gpt-4o-mini",
});
console.log(response.content);

// Streaming
const emitter = ai.chat(
  {
    messages: [{ role: "user", content: "Tell me a story" }],
    stream: true,
  },
  {
    onMessage: (msg) => console.log(msg.content),
    onComplete: (response) => console.log("Done!"),
  }
);

// With tools (auto-routes to agentic service)
const response = await ai.chat({
  messages: [{ role: "user", content: "Show notification" }],
  tools: [
    {
      name: "notify",
      description: "Show notification",
      parameters: {
        type: "object",
        properties: { message: { type: "string" } },
        required: ["message"],
      },
    },
  ],
});
```

#### `generateImage(request, callbacks?)` - Generate Images

```typescript
const result = await ai.generateImage({
  prompt: "A sunset over mountains",
  model: "google/gemini-2.5-flash-image-preview",
});
console.log(result.imageUrl); // base64 data URL

// With reference image
const result = await ai.generateImage({
  prompt: "Transform to oil painting style",
  referenceImages: imageBase64,
});
```

#### `isConfigured()` - Check Authentication

```typescript
if (ai.isConfigured()) {
  console.log("Ready!");
}
```

### Multimodal Support

**Image Analysis:**

```typescript
const response = await ai.chat({
  messages: [
    {
      role: "user",
      content: [
        { type: "text", text: "What's in this image?" },
        { type: "image_url", image_url: { url: imageBase64 } },
      ],
    },
  ],
  model: "openai/gpt-4o",
});
```

**Audio Analysis:**

```typescript
const response = await ai.chat({
  messages: [
    {
      role: "user",
      content: [
        { type: "text", text: "Transcribe this audio" },
        {
          type: "input_audio",
          input_audio: { data: audioBase64, format: "wav" },
        },
      ],
    },
  ],
  model: "google/gemini-2.5-flash",
});
```

