## 🎨 fal.ai Module

Access 100+ production-ready generative media models through fal.ai's unified API.

```typescript
import { fal } from "@canva-ct/genai/fal";
```

### Key Features

- **100+ models**: Image, video, voice, and audio generation
- **Pre-configured auth**: Automatic token injection
- **Lambda endpoint**: 300s timeout for long-running jobs

### Methods

#### `fal.subscribe(modelId, options)` - Queue-based (Recommended)

```typescript
const result = await fal.subscribe("fal-ai/nano-banana-pro", {
  input: {
    prompt: "A cute puppy in pixar style",
    image_size: "square_hd",
    num_images: 1,
  },
  logs: true,
  onQueueUpdate: (update) => {
    if (update.status === "IN_PROGRESS") console.log("Processing...");
  },
});

console.log(result.data.images[0].url);
```

#### `fal.run(modelId, options)` - Direct Execution

```typescript
const result = await fal.run("fal-ai/flux/schnell", {
  input: { prompt: "A beautiful sunset" },
});
```

### Popular Models

| Category             | Models                                                                                                        |
| -------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Image Generation** | `fal-ai/nano-banana-pro`, `fal-ai/flux/schnell`, `fal-ai/flux-pro/v1.1`                                       |
| **Video Generation** | `fal-ai/veo3.1/fast`, `openai/sora-2`, `fal-ai/kling-video/v1/standard/image-to-video`                        |
| **Avatar & Lipsync** | `veed/fabric-1.0`, `creatify/lipsync`, `bytedance/omnihuman/v1.5`, `ai-avatar/single-text`, `sync-lipsync/v2` |
| **Image Editing**    | `fal-ai/nano-banana-pro/edit`, `fal-ai/inpaint`, `fal-ai/rembg`                                               |
| **Audio & Voice**    | `fal-ai/f5-tts`, `fal-ai/whisper`                                                                             |

Explore all models: [fal.ai/explore](https://fal.ai/explore)

### Examples

```typescript
// Generate multiple images
const result = await fal.subscribe("fal-ai/nano-banana-pro", {
  input: { prompt: "Futuristic city", num_images: 1, image_size: "square_hd" },
});

// Image-to-image
const result = await fal.subscribe("fal-ai/flux/dev/image-to-image", {
  input: {
    prompt: "Oil painting style",
    image_url: [imageBase64], // base64 or URL
    strength: 0.75,
  },
});

// Background removal
const result = await fal.run("fal-ai/bria/background/remove", {
  input: { image_url: imageBase64 },
});
```

Explore all models: [fal.ai/explore](https://fal.ai/explore)

