## 🌐 OpenRouter Module

Direct OpenRouter API access for advanced use cases.

```typescript
import { OpenRouterService } from "@canva-ct/genai/openrouter";

const openrouter = new OpenRouterService();
```

### Methods

#### `chat(request)` - Chat Completion

```typescript
// Non-streaming
const response = await openrouter.chat({
  messages: [{ role: "user", content: "Hello!" }],
  model: "openai/gpt-4o",
});
console.log(response.choices[0].message.content);

// Streaming
const emitter = openrouter.chat({
  messages: [{ role: "user", content: "Tell a story" }],
  model: "openai/gpt-4o",
  stream: true,
});
emitter.on("chunk", (r) => console.log(r.choices[0].delta.content));
emitter.on("complete", (r) => console.log("Done"));
```

#### `generateImage(options)` - Image Generation

```typescript
const response = await openrouter.generateImage({
  prompt: "Sunset over mountains",
  model: "google/gemini-2.5-flash-image-preview",
});
```

#### `listModels()` - List Available Models

```typescript
const models = await openrouter.listModels();
models.data.forEach((m) => console.log(m.id, m.name));
```

#### `request(endpoint, method, data?)` - Raw API Access

```typescript
const response = await openrouter.request("/v1/auth/key", "GET");
```

