## 🔊 TTS Module

Text-to-Speech using OpenAI's TTS models.

```typescript
import { TTSService } from "@canva-ct/genai/tts";

const tts = new TTSService();
```

### Methods

#### `speak(options)` - Generate & Play Audio

```typescript
const audio = await tts.speak({
  input: "Hello, world!",
  model: "gpt-4o-mini-tts",
  voice: "coral",
  instructions: "Speak cheerfully",
  autoplay: true,
});

// Manual control
audio.pause();
audio.play();
```

#### `synthesize(options)` - Get Audio Blob

```typescript
const blob = await tts.synthesize({
  input: "Save this audio",
  model: "tts-1-hd",
  voice: "nova",
  response_format: "mp3",
});

// Download
const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
const a = document.createElement("a");
a.href = url;
a.download = "speech.mp3";
a.click();
```

#### `stop()` - Stop Playback

```typescript
tts.stop();
```

### Options

| Models                                 | Voices                                                             | Formats                                    |
| -------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------ |
| `tts-1`, `tts-1-hd`, `gpt-4o-mini-tts` | `alloy`, `ash`, `coral`, `echo`, `nova`, `onyx`, `sage`, `shimmer` | `mp3`, `opus`, `aac`, `flac`, `wav`, `pcm` |

