## 🔗 Integration

This package integrates with:

- **@canva-ct/auth**: Automatic authentication
- **@canva-ct/logger**: Structured logging

## 🐛 Troubleshooting

| Issue                  | Solution                                                |
| ---------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
| Authentication errors  | Call `setupAuth()` before using services                |
| Streaming stuck        | Use `forceReset()` to clear streams                     |
| Image generation fails | Use compatible model (Google Gemini)                    |
| Model not found        | Check [OpenRouter Models](https://openrouter.ai/models) |
